In re 915 GLENGYLE PLACE BUILDING CORPORATION, Debtor. Chester R. DAVIS et al., as Members of the Committee, etc. v. 915 GLENGYLE PLACE BUILDING CORPORATION, et al. No. 6157. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. March 2, 1937. Don Kenneth Jones, John M. Baker, and Tracy W. Buckingham, all of Chicago, 111., for appellants.

Before EVANS and SPARKS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellants, it is now here ordered, adjudged, and decreed by this court that this appeal be and the same is hereby dismissed, without costs.
